cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a new algorithm that combines Reinforcement Learning (RL) with Model Predictive Control (MPC) to learn optimal policies while satisfying constraints. This makes it likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the use of MPC suggests that it could also belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. Finally, the paper demonstrates the effectiveness of the algorithm in playing Atari games, which suggests that it could also belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category.
